  "title": "Food Stall Assistant (Full-Time / Part-Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Prepare and clean food ingredients.</li><li>Prepare simple dishes.</li><li>Take food orders from customers.</li><li>Collect payment, issue receipts and pack orders.</li><li>Keeping work stations clean and tidy.</li><li>Perform Halal compliance checks (including verifying and endorsing incoming ingredients to ensure they meet Halal requirements and are approved by MUIS).</li><li>Any other duties may be assigned on ad hoc basis.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Responsible, disciplined and willing to learn.</li><li>Able to work independently and as part of a team.</li><li>Willing to work shifts, weekends and public holidays.</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced F&B environment.</li><li>This candidate must fulfill the Halal requirements.</li><li>Able to follow Halal procedures as well as food safety and hygiene guidelines.</li><li>Prior experience in F&B is an advantage but not mandatory.</li></ul>",
